  <entry>
    <title>Hexo &amp; Pages = Blog</title>
    <link href="http://naijoug.com/2016/01/11/Hexo%20&amp;%20GitHub%20=%20Blog/"/>
    <id>http://naijoug.com/2016/01/11/Hexo &amp; GitHub = Blog/</id>
    <published>2016-01-11T06:30:07.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-04-15T07:07:45.000Z</updated>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://hexo.io/zh-cn/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Hexo&lt;/a&gt;是一个快速、简洁且高效的博客框架。在线的&lt;code&gt;Git&lt;/code&gt;仓库(&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Github&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://coding.net&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Coding&lt;/a&gt;)都提供了免费的&lt;code&gt;Pages&lt;/code&gt;服务(静态网页托管和发布服务)。两者结合可以迅速的搭建个人站，简略记录一下大致流程。&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
      <category term="Tutorial" scheme="http://naijoug.com/categories/Tutorial/"/>
    
    
